System Requirements
-------------------

The following Perl version and packages are required for...

...building Mail::SPF::Test:

  Perl 5.6
  Module-Build 0.26
  version

...running Mail::SPF::Test:

  Perl 5.6
  version
  NetAddr-IP 4
  Net-DNS 0.58
  YAML

Building and Installing
-----------------------

You can build and install Mail::SPF::Test automatically using the CPAN shell,
or manually with the following commands:

  perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install

